high_descs: Move to the right. Move until you are parallel to the sink. Turn to the left.
Place the bowl in the sink. Turn on the faucet for 7 seconds. Remove the bowl.
Turn your back. Go to where the sidetable is. Turn left to face it.
Place the bowl on the sidetable to the left near the wall.
anns.task_desc: Place the Bowl to the left near the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn right to face the sink.
Wash the bowl in the sink and take the bowl out.
Turn around to walk to the sidetable across the room.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed bowl on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the bowl from the sink.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the bowl into the sink and washed it.
Take it out and go near the side table.
Put the bowl on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the bowl on the side table.
